{"tid":938970,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警掃黃男女攀窗爬水渠逃走 男走甩女受傷","createTime":"2018-12-12T17:16:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-12T17:20:47.000Z","uid":90,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ca949201edd34c939d5a7026470338818fc0e765","tid":938970,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T17:16:13.000Z","msg":"尖沙嘴發生男女墮樓事件，下午4時許，油尖警區特別職務隊於寶勒巷2A號發利大廈進行掃黃行動，其間一名男子由2樓一單位攀窗而出，另一名女子跟隨其後，兩人沿水渠爬落1樓，場面驚險。該名男子其後走至一個招牌再躍下，跳至約3米下的街上離去。而另一名女子其後亦爬至1樓，見無路可逃亦躍至地面，墮地時疑受傷動彈不得。<br />\n<br />\n讀者朱先生表示，當時首先見一名男子跳至街上，懷疑腳部受傷，一拐一拐離開現場，其後女子亦跳至地面，剛巧一名女途人經過，幸未有被壓中。朱生指出，事發大廈有不少一樓一鳳姐單位，估計是警方掃黃期間有人攀窗逃走。<br />\n<br />\n警方表示，下午4時17分接獲一名途人報案，指發現一名29歲姓廖內地女子站於上址一單位外，其後從另一單位墮下至地下。警員接報到場，廖女清醒被送往伊利沙伯醫院治理。警方經初步調查，列有人意外受傷。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MoJzs1u.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMoJzs1u.png&h=f1be141f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HRw5zGD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHRw5zGD.png&h=ccb5ef96&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6qu3mmD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6qu3mmD.png&h=35d6e818&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GS80ozZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGS80ozZ.png&h=03df4816&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20181212/59022130\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181212%2F59022130&d=pNmjKUHxl5ctTJihngLYQwCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=7890061c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181212%2F59022130&h=a05f0c7a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20181212/59022130</a>"},{"pid":"d4053d48b86a0e9aead4e84c71ee9fd86fa92587","tid":938970,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T17:20:47.000Z","msg":"諗到跌落嚟個下好笑"}]}